---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import CTASection from '../components/CTASection.astro';
---

<Layout title="About Tad Scott | Scott Homes Topsail Island" description="Learn about Tad Scott, a Topsail Island real estate professional with decades of local investing, building, mortgage, and Realtor experience.">
  <section class="bg-sand px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-10 lg:grid-cols-[0.8fr_1.2fr] lg:items-center">
      <img class="mx-auto h-[520px] w-full max-w-md rounded-sm object-cover object-top shadow-xl shadow-sky-950/15" src="/assets/tad-scott.webp" alt="Tad Scott" />
      <div>
        <p class="text-sm font-black uppercase tracking-wide text-sky-700">About Tad Scott</p>
        <h1 class="mt-3 text-4xl font-black text-sky-950 sm:text-5xl">Local experience from investing, building, lending, and selling.</h1>
        <div class="mt-6 space-y-5 text-base leading-8 text-slate-650">
          <p>I began investing in coastal real estate in 1999 and soon after started building homes on the island. In 2000, I founded my own mortgage company. Over the past two decades as a real estate investor, builder, and now a Realtor, I have watched the local market from several angles.</p>
          <p>My approach is practical and thorough. I treat each listing as if it were my own property, with attention to pricing, photos, presentation, open houses, and communication with active local agents.</p>
          <p>For buyers and new construction clients, that same background helps with questions around location, home condition, lot selection, builder quality, rental potential, and long-term value.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="px-4 py-14 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="mx-auto grid max-w-7xl gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      {[
        ['Investor perspective', 'Tad has personally studied coastal real estate as an owner, investor, and market participant since 1999.'],
        ['Builder perspective', 'New construction experience helps clients understand lots, materials, plans, timelines, and practical tradeoffs.'],
        ['Listing perspective', 'Selling strategy focuses on local pricing, strong visual presentation, open houses, and steady follow-through.'],
      ].map(([title, text]) => (
        <article class="rounded-sm border border-sky-950/10 bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
          <h2 class="text-xl font-black text-sky-950">{title}</h2>
          <p class="mt-3 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-600">{text}</p>
        </article>
      ))}
    </div>
  </section>

  <CTASection eyebrow="Work with local context" title="Talk through your Topsail plans with Tad." />
</Layout>
